heroclass.name: Ranger
heroclass.desc:
Rangers can gain a special pet, which can find items and give reward bonuses.
Use the pet command to see pet options.

heroclass.name: Wizard
heroclass.desc:
Wizards have the option to focus and add large bonuses to their magic, but their focus can sometimes go astray...
Use the focus command when attacking in an adventure.

Use the rage command when attacking in an adventure.
